org.gbif.common.messaging.api.messages

Class OccurrenceMutatedMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gbif.common.messaging.api.messages.OccurrenceMutatedMessage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Message, DatasetBasedMessage

    public class OccurrenceMutatedMessage
extends Object
implements DatasetBasedMessage
    The message sent whenever an "interpreted" occurrence has changed (either NEW, UPDATED, or DELETED). An interpreted occurrence is the result of interpreting the values of a verbatim occurrence.
